<br>
&quot;We help others, and contain people who help others, and try to lead the populace by being a good example. By defeating those who act against the young and the ideals of objective good (which is quite a different thing from classic EQ &quot;good&quot;), and aiding young ones (who aren't necessarily in the guild), we promote a better Norrath, free of past prejudices.&quot;<br>
<br>
